{"tid":335703,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［無圖］好似係耳機鋪比人當左狗公","createTime":"2017-07-25T19:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T19:15:16.000Z","uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08682fec200de3106512ae767cd107c76d30d5cb","tid":335703,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"個朋友同我講<br />\n佢同另外個fd尋晚去旺角某耳機鋪試耳機<br />\n咁試試下 見到有個女仔個耳機同佢一樣<br />\n咁個女仔就想買升級線啦<br />\n而個fd咁岩幾日前試過一條好正既線<br />\n條線係熟人自己造出黎既 賣得平過市面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以喱條傻仔就抱住救人既心態<br />\n諗住搵機會同個女仔講 佢識人整升級線平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後係失敗架 因為啲店員係附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而件事完左之後 個朋友既朋友同返 我個朋友講<br />\n個女仔成程笑得好假 答得好敷衍<br />\n仲要以求救既眼神望住佢 好似想叫個fd收嗲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個朋友表示 成件事錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8840519751429e2ac25b6c6b8f71b5d8d928a577","tid":335703,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T19:39:21.000Z","msg":"女人: 覺得好奇怪囉"},{"pid":"00db6203496050746e45b783ab8e070235a5476f","tid":335703,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T20:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人: 覺得好奇怪囉</blockquote><br />\n其實都係 無啦啦有個男仔行埋黎搭嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個朋友就係衰突然有自信 平時佢唔會咁架"},{"pid":"bddedf497e12c68ad4828514bdf5bba4725be290","tid":335703,"uid":8786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:14:25.000Z","msg":"：個日我入去諗住求其買返條綫用啦～點知有個毒男走埋黎叫我去第二度買wo,我心諗勁awkward囉～"},{"pid":"4854c675d1fe069e636739624da304dbcfe4d37b","tid":335703,"uid":38623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"根本就係狗公 如果果個係暗瘡肥婆仲會唔會搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78122eb881e13a369e3a480d1e6791ec4889f1aa","tid":335703,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:18:38.000Z","msg":"Your face your fate"},{"pid":"d17e7ecb2ccd201774152c7f201abe65acca95dd","tid":335703,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece8885a53f47088bf0cb9ee3feb45b8f642d6c5","tid":335703,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:22:56.000Z","msg":"hand hand"},{"pid":"8ce065d8deba8f3d1b74b3b5c0e4f49a9c83ccc4","tid":335703,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T01:25:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌"},{"pid":"40e6bb1c2b6e316b7e35e8ae32c1f78a9d20bb33","tid":335703,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就係狗公 如果果個係暗瘡肥婆仲會唔會搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我相信暗瘡肥婆無人想救佢出坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但正常樣既話 我諗大部分人都願意伸出援手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45b286c55a168a032c3b6c420b7304fe0b89e58","tid":335703,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚最忌</blockquote><br />\n最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我會提下個朋友架啦<br />\n叫佢學下我咁"},{"pid":"068bddd1ae75d25bbf9d7788873cb7901e32d812","tid":335703,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Your face your fate</blockquote>一言驚醒夢中人"}]}